"  return `Hello ${name}!`;\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: src/en/modules/ROOT/pages/team-collaboration-review.adoc:25
msgid ""
"If you are using TypeScript for code documentation, you can add the "
